#Insertion sort.

##Codigo
1. for (j <- 1 to A.length - 1) 
   {
2.     key = A(j)
3.     i = j - 1
4.      while (i >= 0 && A(i) > key) 
        {
5.        A(i + 1) = A(i)
6.        i = i - 1
        }
7.      A(i + 1) = key
      }
   }
